summary: Hi, and welcome to Reasons Why I Need Therapy #1
body:
Hi, and welcome to Reasons Why I Need Therapy #1

My goal is to marry someone who will make me happier than what Dan and Phil have made me.

That’s going to be quite a challenge, seeing as Dan and Phil are the reason I’m happy again in the first place.
